# Agents Tracker - {{CUSTOMER_NAME}}

This file tracks agent-level metadata for FDE engagement weekly tracker submissions. It serves as the single source of truth for stable agent information that doesn't change frequently.

**Purpose**: Store persistent agent metadata to streamline weekly form submissions. Combined with change logs from `/project-sync`, this enables `/fde-tracker-submit` to auto-generate form-ready output.

**Maintenance**: Update this file when agent details change (new agents, phase transitions, go-live dates, etc.). The `/project-sync` skill can help keep this updated from meeting notes and Slack messages.

